RE Enpower cost allocation Cc I have set up a conference call for today Oct nd at pm central time for dialins Dial in number Passcode Thank you Claudia Guerra East Power Trading EBC off fax Original Message From Will Lloyd Sent Monday October PM To Guerra Claudia Cc Belden Tim Zufferli John Presto Kevin M Subject RE Enpower cost allocation Claudia please arrange a conference call with Tim John and myself to discuss the method for allocation going forward Please note that John is in Calgary and has a hour time difference and Tim is in Seattle with a hour time difference Thanks Original Message From Belden Tim Sent Monday October PM To Zufferli John Will Lloyd Presto Kevin M Subject RE Enpower cost allocation I am amenable to many different allocation methods I think that John has a good point John the allocation for Canada includes both Toronto and Calgary However there is also an argument that there should be some fixed component and a transactionbased component I think that we need to come up with one methodology that applies to Canada West and East What methodology do you guys want to use Original Message From Zufferli John Sent Monday October AM To Will Lloyd Belden Tim Milnthorp Rob Subject Enpower cost allocation Since Alberta Power trades timesday and East and West power trade in excess of timesday I believe that a allocation for my desk is inappropriate I would be willing to settle for and I believe that this is more that generation
